<td><pre>     * @param ex</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="50"></td><td><pre>     * @throws Exception</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="51"></td><td><pre>     */</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="52"></td><td><pre>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">afterCompletion</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token class-name">HttpServletRequest</span> request<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token class-name">HttpServletResponse</span> response<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token class-name">Object</span> handler<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token class-name">Exception</span> ex<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">throws</span> <span class="token class-name">Exception</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="53"></td><td><pre>        <span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">getClass</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">getName</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">"---afterCompletion2"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="54"></td><td><pre>    <span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="55"></td><td><pre><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>springmvc 配置</p><figure class="highlight xml"><figcaption data-lang="XML"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num="1"></td><td><pre><span class="token comment">&lt;!-- 拦截器 --></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="2"></td><td><pre>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span><span class="token namespace">mvc:</span>interceptors</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="3"></td><td><pre>        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>bean</span> <span class="token attr-name">class</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>com.fan.interceptor.MyInterceptor<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>bean</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="4"></td><td><pre>        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>bean</span> <span class="token attr-name">class</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>com.fan.interceptor.MyInterceptor2<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>bean</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="5"></td><td><pre>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span><span class="token namespace">mvc:</span>interceptors</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其余不变进行测试：可以看到根据 springmvc 中配置拦截器的先后顺序来执行，后配置的拦截器被套在了最里面执行完毕之后，前定义的拦截器才会继续执行。</p><p><img data-src="https://gitee.com/bfanfanfan/img/raw/master/docsify/image-20201127132939678.png" alt="image-20201127132939678"></p><p><img data-src="https://gitee.com/bfanfanfan/img/raw/master/docsify/image-20201127132958527.png" alt="image-20201127132958527"></p><h2 id="拦截器跟过滤器的区别"><a class="anchor" href="#拦截器跟过滤器的区别">#</a> 拦截器跟过滤器的区别</h2><p>​ 1、过滤器是基于函数回调的，而拦截器是基于 java 反射的</p><p>​ 2、过滤器依赖于 servlet 容器，而拦截器不依赖与 Servlet 容器</p><p>​ 3、连接器几乎对所有的请求都起作用和，而拦截器只能对 action 请求起作用</p><p>​ 4、拦截器可以访问 action 的上下文，而过滤器不可以</p><p>​ 5、在 action 的生命周期中，拦截器可以多次调用，而过滤器只能在容器初始化的时候调用一次</p><p><img data-src="https://gitee.com/bfanfanfan/img/raw/master/docsify/%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8%E8%B7%9F%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B-1606455498366.png" alt=""></p><p><img data-src="https://gitee.com/bfanfanfan/img/raw/master/docsify/%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8%E5%92%8C%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB.png" alt="拦截器和过滤器的包含关系"></p><h2 id="springmvc的国际化"><a class="anchor" href="#springmvc的国际化">#</a> SpringMVC 的国际化</h2><p>所谓国际化就是选择不同的语言后显示的页面内容语言不同。由于浏览器本身自带的翻译效果无法精准传递我们需要表达的信息，所以一般在开发中都会自定义国际化资源配置文件，并通过代码实现让用户在浏览器切换不同的语言时加载我们提前配置好的国际化资源文件，从而传递我们想要传递的信息，提升用户体验。</p><h3 id="springmvc提供的国际化机制"><a class="anchor" href="#springmvc提供的国际化机制">#</a> springmvc 提供的国际化机制</h3><p>通过 springmvc 提供的国际化机制来实现国际化。</p><p>添加依赖：</p><p>该依赖是为了在 login.jsp 中使用 fmt 标签</p><figure class="highlight xml"><figcaption data-lang="XML"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num="1"></td><td><pre><span class="token comment">&lt;!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/javax.servlet/jstl --></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="2"></td><td><pre>        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>dependency</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="3"></td><td><pre>            <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>groupId</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>javax.servlet<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>groupId</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="4"></td><td><pre>            <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>artifactId</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>jstl<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>artifactId</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="5"></td><td><pre>            <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>version</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>1.2<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>version</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="6"></td><td><pre>        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>dependency</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>login.jsp：</p><p>注意：添加声明 &lt;%@ taglib prefix=&quot;fmt&quot; uri=&quot;<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cDovL2phdmEuc3VuLmNvbS9qc3AvanN0bC9mbXQ=">http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/fmt</span>&quot; %&gt;</p><pre><code class="language-jsp">&lt;%--
  Created by IntelliJ IDEA.
  User: MB248
  Date: 2020-10-16
  Time: 11:19
