该注解中的 value 值代表异常类型。</p><p>error.jsp:</p><pre><code class="language-jsp">&lt;%--
  Created by IntelliJ IDEA.
  User: MB248
  Date: 2020-10-20
  Time: 10:21
  To change this template use File | Settings | File Templates.
--%&gt;
