oller</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95-3"><span class="toc-number">3.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">测试</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#httpentity%E4%B8%8Eresponseentity"><span class="toc-number">4.</span> <span class="toc-text">HttpEntity 与 ResponseEntity</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#requestentityjsp"><span class="toc-number">4.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">requestEntity.jsp</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#controller-4"><span class="toc-number">4.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">controller</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95-4"><span class="toc-number">4.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">测试</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD"><span class="toc-number">5.</span> <span class="toc-text">文件下载</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#controller-5"><span class="toc-number">5.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">controller</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95-5"><span class="toc-number">5.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">测试</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0"><span class="toc-number">6.</span> <span class="toc-text">文件上传</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96jar%E5%8C%85"><span class="toc-number">6.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">依赖 jar 包</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#springmvc%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6"><span class="toc-number">6.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">springmvc 配置文件</span></a></li><li cl